Class Coord.Unique

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.Unique<Coord>
      • model.Coord.Unique
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Viewable<Coord.View>, Coord.Interface.ReadOnly, Coord.Interface.ReadWrite
    Enclosing class:
    Coord

    public static final class Coord.Unique
extends Unique<Coord>
implements Coord.Interface.ReadWrite, Viewable<Coord.View>
    By implementing Unique, Coord.Unique tells us it contains a Coord that no one can have modifiable references to until it is taken.
